---
title: Carb Smart Halloumi and Clementine Salad with Mint, Almonds and Croutons
description: Golden seared halloumi lends a salty, creamy bite to this fresh and bright salad. Clementine brings juicy sweetness, while croutons and almonds give texture and crunch!
